1
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:08,040
ALI: We're going to be fine, guys. Just a little turbulence.

2
00:00:08,040 --> 00:00:10,800
SAM: Ali, what's going on? We're falling or something!

3
00:00:10,800 --> 00:00:14,856
LEO: Dude, relax. It's just a bump. We'll be fine.

4
00:00:14,856 --> 00:00:22,272
ABEEHA: Everyone, please fasten your seatbelts and return to your seats. We apologize for the inconvenience.

5
00:00:22,272 --> 00:00:28,272
ALI: Abeeha, can you please get the passengers to calm down? We don't need a panic.

6
00:00:28,272 --> 00:00:31,920
ABEEHA: Of course, Ali. I'm on it.

7
00:00:31,920 --> 00:00:36,226
ALI: Hold on, guys. This is going to get bumpy.

8
00:00:36,226 --> 00:00:39,178
SAM: Ali, what's happening? We're going to crash or something!

9
00:00:39,178 --> 00:00:43,306
LEO: Ali, tell us what's going on. We need to know what's happening.

10
00:00:43,306 --> 00:00:50,578
ABEEHA: Everyone, please return to your seats and fasten your seatbelts. We're experiencing some turbulence.

11
00:00:50,578 --> 00:00:56,396
ALI: Abeeha, I need to level the plane. Can you get the passengers to calm down?

12
00:00:56,396 --> 00:01:01,868
ABEEHA: Ali, I'm trying, but they're getting scared. What can I do to help?

13
00:01:01,868 --> 00:01:06,884
ALI: Just keep them calm. I need to focus on flying this thing.
